ca.uqac.lif.ecp

Class TWayScoringTraceGenerator<T extends Event>

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uqac.lif.ecp.TraceGenerator<T>
      • ca.uqac.lif.ecp.TWayScoringTraceGenerator<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the events in the traces that are generated

    public class TWayScoringTraceGenerator<T extends Event>
extends TraceGenerator<T>
    A t-way trace generator. This is an implementation of the t-sequence algorithm in the book Introduction to Combinatorial Testing, Figure 10.1.
    Author:
    Sylvain
